<item>
            <title>[LU-1551] FYI: Contollers on storage1 and storage 2 have both crashed at University of Delaware</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1551</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Are there a known issues with Wham cloud configuration that would cause RAID controllers to fail. It seems that the customer has encountered two failures on two separate storage systems. We are currently working with U Del to determine if this issue is hardware vs software related failure.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
