                            <comment id="41228" author="cliffw" created="Wed, 27 Jun 2012 22:15:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;What is your current state?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="41011" author="cliffw" created="Thu, 21 Jun 2012 16:28:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There are no issues with Lustre that should cause a storage controller to fail. However Lustre does generate a high volume of IO and we have seen some instances in the past where hardware has struggled to keep up.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
